description: I'm a traveller and a software developer. I love to travel mostly in hill areas and also in historical areas. Besides travelling and developing softwares, I love to taste different kinds of foods of different cultures and countries.

posts.title: Himachal e Hattogol
posts.description: This was an impressive tour in my life. First time I went outside of my country for tour. It was about 2 weeks journey. I travelled with my 15 other friends. We explored Shimla, Manali, Kasol, Delhi, Agra & Kolkata.
